{"tid":161491,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"傳巴塞隆拿5000萬鎊斟藍斯","createTime":"2017-03-18T14:36:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-29T14:16:44.000Z","uid":19552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bdad4fd7eaa4a93027116d6d59a92597a0e0b67c","tid":161491,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T14:36:38.000Z","msg":"西甲班霸巴塞隆拿準備夏天轉會市場出手，以巨額收購阿仙奴中場艾朗藍斯，以及求購愛華頓中堅史東斯。<br />\n<br />\n巴塞隆拿有意「打包」收購艾朗藍斯及史東斯強化實力。<br />\n<br />\n周日快報消息指出，巴塞想斥資5000萬鎊斟藍斯，同時想購入史東斯。據知雲格也留意到巴塞教頭安歷基對於藍斯虎視眈眈。(<a href=\"http://Goal.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FGoal.com&d=ualpl%2FmkMQCwG5JKQRKj7Izu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=7ee46ac9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Goal.com</a>)"},{"pid":"0ebdd63cdaf6bdd11d69bbed09067d6958575c94","tid":161491,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T14:38:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c65dcb819501ed9aec9eb4ab7186fc34f585bab","tid":161491,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T14:38:53.000Z","msg":"4年前？"},{"pid":"2bd7f5da7db94851fe97db47a954093436ee0467","tid":161491,"uid":30040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T14:39:54.000Z","msg":"5000萬掟落咸水海"},{"pid":"1dd262fadf53a4ba7041cd77937f55c726bb3d1b","tid":161491,"uid":993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T14:41:46.000Z","msg":"用左35m買高美斯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9193540d4160029fb30850cd9b3c373934385cfd","tid":161491,"uid":1790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T14:49:44.000Z","msg":"史東斯好野黎 識用波既中堅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e116740a0bc9d9dca8698b0eb159c923546ff55","tid":161491,"uid":66651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T17:19: